data.description: Welcome to 1020 Albatross Lane! This coastal residence is nestled in the heart of the Planters Pointe neighborhood, offering proximity to the full array of everything Mount Pleasant has to offer. Recently updated, this home boasts a contemporary aesthetic with freshly installed plumbing fixtures and luxury vinyl flooring on both the first floor and upstairs bathrooms. Peace of mind is assured as significant systems have also been recently replaced including HVAC system and a water heater installed in 2023, coupled with a roof replacement in 2021. The main level encompasses a cozy living room adorned with a gas fireplace, seamlessly flowing into a dedicated dining area. The luminous kitchen exudes an open and airy ambiance, adorned with granite countertops, soft-close cabinets, and a suite of stainless steel appliances. All of the bedrooms are thoughtfully situated on the second floor, accompanied by a generously sized bonus room. The versatile bonus space could serve as a secondary family area or even a fourth bedroom. The outdoor space features a new concrete patio, providing an ideal retreat for relaxation. Additionally, the sale of the property includes the golf cart shown in the photos, perfect for conveniently cruising to the neighborhood amenities center which include a pool, tennis/pickleball courts, a basketball court, and playground. Come take a look at everything that this great opportunity has to offer today!
